{"id": "1232676068020719687", "channel_id": "1232672747633639434", "type": 0, "author_id": "699270788578148442", "author_name": "_buqi", "author_bot": false, "content": "可能描述不夠仔細吧\n觸手算非主動傷害\n蟲群意識、我們的家都有特別描述造成主動傷害", "timestamp": "2024-04-24T12:54:36.630000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-04-24T12:54:51.021000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1232672747633639434", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」节日祝福有bug", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960"]}
{"id": "1232676425182613525", "channel_id": "1232672747633639434", "type": 0, "author_id": "597345991632486406", "author_name": "whimsical_starfish_19845", "author_bot": false, "content": "我之前稍微觀察過幾次 深海以前是表面上觸手不觸發 次數也不跳 但實質上會觸發", "timestamp": "2024-04-24T12:56:01.784000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1232672747633639434", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」节日祝福有bug", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960"]}
{"id": "1232676463531134999", "channel_id": "1232672747633639434", "type": 0, "author_id": "597345991632486406", "author_name": "whimsical_starfish_19845", "author_bot": false, "content": "不過我不能肯定 畢竟沒數據", "timestamp": "2024-04-24T12:56:10.927000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1232672747633639434", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」节日祝福有bug", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960"]}
{"id": "1232676671497306112", "channel_id": "1232672747633639434", "type": 19, "author_id": "1192150433255399548", "author_name": "1035261013", "author_bot": false, "content": "…………\n这个问题是4.18鲨鱼热修的时候我在官群7群看到无一君大佬提出来的，他一更新立刻就发现了，并问了校猫。\n校猫的回复是没有更改计划，他们check一下。\n我觉得这种校猫已经承认的bug就没有必要找补了吧……\n我只是好奇为什么这次没修复", "timestamp": "2024-04-24T12:57:00.510000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["699270788578148442"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1232676068020719687", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1232672747633639434", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」节日祝福有bug", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960"]}
